data.description: What a rare find!  One story home on 1 acre.  Tranquil setting at the end of a culdesac. Very well maintained and updated interior. Full basement provides even more living space. Large, covered deck overlooks beautiful backyard and farm field. Home includes a whole house generator. Don't forget the 30x30 heated pole barn with concrete floor. Great house, great location, don't miss this one!
